Wow, talk about missing the point of the class.  It's one of the class-defining abilities, you know.
<br />

<br />
These days I play another class (Magician).  Every time I group with an enchanter who does nothing but mez and buff, I feel like we wasted a group slot.  I would rather have a shaman in group who can heal as well as haste or a beastlord who can do terrific damage and give us great mana regen (especially since these stack with KEI, which we can get from Buffs R Us in PoK).  Both of these classes can slow faster than enchanters, and the shaman or I can debuff resists better than an enchanter.
<br />

<br />
