Heck, just make a fixed duration 3 minute charm that poofs the pet when charm wears off.  
<br />

<br />
That way you can't get his experience, and raids can't cheeze a pet with multiple enchanters.
<br />

<br />
Some people might object to it being too safe.  I'd counter with the argument that it's not sustainable like the existing charm is, and you are trading time spent finding pets for safety.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
